# WildPointer Website Content Structure Specification

Version: 1.0

## Goal

Define the content file structure for the WildPointer website.

The website must be content-driven. Pages should not contain hardcoded project, role, or SDLC data.

Cursor must implement Astro Content Collections so that new content can be added by creating or editing Markdown / MDX files.

---

# Content Directory

Use the following structure:

```text
src/content/
  projects/
    notes-ai.md
    ai-interview-assistant.md

  stages/
    idea-forming.md
    discovery.md
    product-design.md
    planning.md
    architecture.md
    backlog.md
    development.md
    qa.md
    delivery.md
    operations.md
    feedback.md

  roles/
    vision-lead.md
    coordinator.md
    community-steward.md
    product-lead.md
    maintainer.md

  documents/
    manifesto.md
    roles.md
    sdlc.md
    coordinator-instruction.md
```

---

# Astro Content Collections

Create:

```text
src/content/config.ts
```

Use collections:

* projects
* stages
* roles
* documents

