# TypeScript Requirements

Create TypeScript types or infer them from Astro Content Collections.

Required helper functions:

```ts
getAllProjects()
getFeaturedProjects()
getProjectsByStage(stageSlug)
getAllStages()
getStageBySlug(slug)
getAllRoles()
getRoleBySlug(slug)
getAllDocuments()
```

Sorting rules:

* stages by order
* roles by order
* projects by featured first, then order, then title
* documents by category, then order

