# Routing Requirements

Pages must use content collections.

## Projects

```text
/projects
/projects/[slug]
```

Project profile pages are generated from:

```text
src/content/projects/*.md
```

## SDLC

```text
/sdlc
/sdlc/[stage]
```

Stage pages are generated from:

```text
src/content/stages/*.md
```

## Roles

```text
/roles
/roles/[slug]
```

Role pages are generated from:

```text
src/content/roles/*.md
```

## Documents

Optional:

```text
/docs
/docs/[slug]
```

Document pages are generated from:

```text
src/content/documents/*.md
```

