# Content Validation

Cursor must configure schema validation in:

```text
src/content/config.ts
```

Validation requirements:

* required strings must not be empty
* stage must be one of allowed stage slugs
* status must be one of allowed project statuses
* order must be number
* featured must be boolean
* links and contacts must be optional objects
* arrays must default to empty arrays where possible

