# Acceptance Criteria

The task is complete when:

1. All content collections are created.
2. Content schema validation works.
3. Projects are rendered from Markdown files.
4. SDLC stages are rendered from Markdown files.
5. Roles are rendered from Markdown files.
6. Documents are rendered from Markdown files or listed from collection data.
7. Adding a new project Markdown file automatically creates a new project page.
8. Home page uses featured projects from content collection.
9. SDLC navigation uses stage content collection.
10. No project, stage, role or document data is hardcoded inside page templates.
